devices=`adb devices | awk '/List of devices attached/ { while(getline > 0) { print }}' | grep 'device' | grep -v 'emulator' | awk '{ print $1; }'`
device_list=($devices)
if [[ ${#device_list[@]} > 0 ]] ; then
    for i in ${devices[@]}
    do
        echo $i
    done
    exit 0
else
    echo "No devices found."
    exit 2
fi
